data.title: Cook County Treasurer Maria Pappas will honor Black History Month with an art exhibit and awards for Black leaders.
data.description: In Chicago on February 27, 2026, Cook County Treasurer Maria Pappas will be joined by the African Line Dancers of St. Benedict for a Black History Month celebration at the Cook County Treasurer's Office.
